2013年7月3日，[[史雲斯|史雲斯]]以500萬英鎊簽下舒爾維。<ref>{{cite news |title=Swansea City complete £5m Jonjo Shelvey signing |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/23143710 |work=BBC Sport |date=2013-07-03 |accessdate=2020-02-19 |archive-date=2018-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912135728/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/23143710 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 紐卡素 ===
2016年1月12日，[[紐卡素|紐卡素]]以1200萬英鎊簽下舒爾維，簽下五年半的合約。<ref>{{cite news |title=Jonjo Shelvey: Newcastle sign Swansea midfielder for £12m |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35290127 |work=BBC Sport |date=2016-01-12 |accessdate=2020-02-19 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206093823/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35290127 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

